PhysicModels

Mettre BicicleKinematic avec slide angle \beta en passant lr, lf en param
Faire heriter RearBicicleKinematic en mettant lr = 0 et lf = L => slide angle \beta = 0
Faire heriter FrontBicicleKinematic en mettant lr = L et lf = 0 => slide angle \beta = wheel angle
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HqNdBiej23I&list=PLW3FM5Kyc2_4PGkumkAHNXzWtgHhaYe1d&index=4
